  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Being offline should not prevent user from using the application however we need to standartize the flow for all the screens. When I try to sign transaction while being offline I receive not user friendly red pop-up that should be changed to the standart we apllied to the app.\r\n\r\nMoreover I suggest to disable the `Sign Transaction` button when there is no internet connection\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nAndroid\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/31680629-88421434-b37d-11e7-9f1c-60cb729c412b.png)\r\n\r\niOS even doesnt have the notification\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/31682394-99f822fe-b382-11e7-9047-3772f1d0d1f0.png)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Turn off the internet\r\n- Proceed with sending transaction\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: branch '0.9.10-253-gea9e0055+`\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n* TF https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/6881676/sessions/1/?accessToken=UxV8re71z6s9axRhrQLHvbPsnis",
